[49m[38;5;10m+    192[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    193[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    194[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    195[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare benefits navigator bot decomposes into nine logical stages: channel entry, input safety screening, identity-and-relationship verification, benefits-context loading, intent classification, grounded retrieval and tool orchestration, structured cost-estimate computation, output safety screening with citation verification, and member-services routing for out-of-scope cases. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.4 carry forward; this recipe adds three new ones (plan-document-versioning lifecycle, benefits-data-source freshness governance, regulatory-disclosure-phrasings library).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY ─────────────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Member opens chat in payer's app, payer's website,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    member-services portal, or employer-side benefits      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    site; or front-desk staff opens the bot in the         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    practice's benefits-verification tool]                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Greeting and disclosure]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Identifies as a chatbot                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - States scope (informational benefits questions;      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      not making coverage decisions; not replacing         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      member-services for complex cases)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acknowledges that emergencies should go to 911       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Offers an immediate path to a human counselor        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate session_id                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture channel, authentication context, deep-link   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      parameters (e.g., a specific claim or bill the       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      member tapped to start the conversation)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context, deep-link   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    parameters]                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY SCREENING ────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Same primitive as the previous chapter 11 recipes,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    with benefits-specific tuning:]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis detection (members occasionally disclose      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      crisis when asking about behavioral-health           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      benefits or when distressed about a denial)          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Financial-distress detection (members who describe   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      not being able to pay a bill route to financial-     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      assistance counseling rather than only to billing)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: input passes / input blocked-with-disposition] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── IDENTITY AND RELATIONSHIP VERIFICATION ────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Authenticated session path (recommended default)]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Member is logged into the payer's app or portal      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Session conveys verified member_id and plan_id       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Unauthenticated link path]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For lower-stakes questions (general plan info,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      provider search) the bot may answer without          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      authentication, with reduced data scope              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Member-specific questions (claims, deductible,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      prior-auth) require step-up authentication           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Family-relationship handling]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - When the member is the subscriber and asks about     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      a covered family member (spouse, child), the bot     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      verifies the family relationship and the             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      subscriber's authorized scope (e.g., parents have    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reduced access to teenagers' records under state-    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      specific minor-consent rules)                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Authorized-representative handling]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - HIPAA personal representatives, court-appointed      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      guardians, members who have designated a third-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      party have the appropriate access scope              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: verified member_id, plan_id, family_scope,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    representative_relationship, assurance_level]          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
