[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Plan year and effective dates                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Network tiers                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Deductible and out-of-pocket-max architecture        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cost-share structure (copays, coinsurance,           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tiers)                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Plan-specific exclusions and limits                  │
