[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Embedded vs aggregate family logic                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Separate medical and pharmacy accumulators           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - As-of date stamp                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: subscriber_context_lookup]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family members covered                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family-relationship structure                        │
