[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: structured plan context, accumulator state,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    subscriber context]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INTENT CLASSIFICATION ─────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Classify the member's question into a benefits-        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    intent category with confidence:]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - coverage_question                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - network_status_question                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - deductible_balance_question                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - claim_explanation_question                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - prior_auth_status_question                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - cost_estimate_question                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - formulary_or_medication_question                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - plan_document_question                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - appeal_or_grievance_intent                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - financial_assistance_intent                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - clinical_question (route out of scope)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - general_chat                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Routing logic]                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - High confidence + in-scope: proceed to retrieval     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Low confidence: ask clarifying question              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Out-of-scope: route to member services or            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appropriate redirect                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appeal/grievance/complex-case intent: route to       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      human counselor with context                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    328[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    329[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    330[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: intent category, intent confidence, routing    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    331[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    decision]                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    332[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    333[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    334[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    335[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── GROUNDED RETRIEVAL AND TOOL ORCHESTRATION ─────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    336[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    337[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-intent tool selection]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    338[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - coverage_question → plan_document_retrieval +        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    339[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coverage_lookup                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    340[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - network_status_question → provider_network_lookup    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    341[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - deductible_balance_question → accumulator_lookup     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    342[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - claim_explanation_question → claim_lookup +          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    343[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      carc_rarc_translation                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    344[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - prior_auth_status_question → prior_auth_lookup       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    345[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - cost_estimate_question → cost_estimate_compute       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    346[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - formulary_or_medication_question →                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      formulary_lookup                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - plan_document_question → plan_document_retrieval     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    350[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Plan-document retrieval]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    351[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retrieval scoped to: plan_id + plan_year             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    352[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retrieval returns document chunks plus metadata      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    353[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (document version, effective date, section ref)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Chunks granular enough for citation but coherent     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      enough for understanding                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Member-specific data retrieval]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each tool has a defined source-of-truth system       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    359[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (eligibility-system, claims-system, accumulator-     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    360[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      system, prior-auth-system, formulary-system,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    361[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      provider-network-system)                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    362[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tools return structured data with as-of date         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    363[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      stamps                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    364[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tools return a defined fallback when source-of-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    365[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      truth is unreachable ("I'm having trouble pulling    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    366[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      that data right now; would you like to wait or       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    367[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      have someone call you back?")                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    368[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    369[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation loop]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    370[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot poses or refines the question                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    371[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Member answers / asks follow-up                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    372[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot retrieves additional facts or escalates          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    373[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot composes grounded response                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    374[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    375[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    376[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: retrieved evidence, structured tool results]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    377[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    379[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── COST-ESTIMATE COMPUTATION ─────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: cost_estimate_compute]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Inputs: service_code, provider_id (optional),        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      member_accumulator_state, plan_cost_share_rules,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      negotiated_rate (where available)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Outputs: estimated_member_cost (range), breakdown    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (deductible_applied, coinsurance_applied, copay,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      OOP-max_impact), as-of date, confidence_level,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caveat_text (estimate not binding, etc.)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: aeob_or_gfe_lookup (where applicable)]           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Returns the formal Advanced EOB or Good Faith        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      Estimate document if one has been generated for      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      this scheduled service                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Caveats embedded in every estimate]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Estimate based on as-of date accumulator state       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Estimate not a binding price                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Actual cost depends on what gets coded and           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adjudicated                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For scheduled services, the provider can give a      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      formal estimate (Good Faith Estimate or Advanced     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      EOB where applicable)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    406[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: structured cost estimate with caveats]         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    407[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    408[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    410[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── OUTPUT SAFETY SCREENING WITH CITATION CHECK ───┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    411[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    412[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Same primitive as the other chapter 11 recipes,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    413[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    with benefits-specific checks:]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    414[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no clinical advice; no binding         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coverage commitments; no diagnostic speculation;     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      no off-label drug recommendations)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    417[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    418[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation verification: every coverage assertion      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    419[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      cited to a retrieved plan-document chunk; every      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    420[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      member-specific assertion cited to a tool result;    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    421[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      every cost number traceable to the cost-estimate     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    422[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tool's output                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Plan-version stamp consistency: cited document       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    424[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      version matches the member's current plan year       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    425[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Regulatory-disclosure inclusion: required            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    426[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      phrasings (state-specific complaint rights,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      No Surprises Act references where applicable,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      parity-law disclosures for behavioral-health         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      questions, appeal rights for denial questions)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    430[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      present where mandated                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persona-and-tone check: empathetic for billing       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      distress, clear for procedural questions             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    434[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared for delivery, replaced with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    436[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    a safer template, or regenerated with corrections]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    437[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── MEMBER-SERVICES ROUTING ───────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    441[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    442[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trigger conditions for human handoff:]                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appeal or grievance intent                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    444[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Complex case (formal coverage exception, medical     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    445[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      necessity dispute, surprise-bill dispute)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    446[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Identity-related issue (lost card, name change,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    447[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      enrollment correction, COBRA-eligibility-event)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    448[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Financial-assistance request                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    449[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis flag                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    450[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-attempt failure (the bot has tried to answer   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    451[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and the member is not satisfied)                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    452[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Member explicitly requests a human                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    453[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    454[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Handoff payload]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    455[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    456[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retrieved evidence                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    457[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool-call results                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    458[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Identified intent and unresolved issue               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    459[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Member's preferred contact method and time           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    460[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acuity flags                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    461[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    462[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Routing target selection]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    463[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - General member services                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    464[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appeals-and-grievances team                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    465[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Behavioral-health benefits team                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    466[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Financial-counseling team                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    467[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis pathway (988 / institutional crisis line)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    470[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: human-handoff event with structured payload]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    471[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    472[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    473[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── AUDIT, LOG, AND TELEMETRY ─────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    476[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Durable conversation record]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User utterances                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated bot responses                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    480[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active plan-document version stamps                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active formulary version stamps                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active provider-network snapshot stamps              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Identity-verification outcome and assurance level    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    485[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family-relationship and representative scope         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition (resolved-by-bot, handed-off,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      member-abandoned, crisis-routed)                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    489[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Benefits-decision-record journal]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    490[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Durable, separately-governed record of every         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    491[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coverage-or-cost answer the bot gave: the member,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    492[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the question, the answer, the cited evidence, the    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      version stamps, the as-of dates                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to the longer of plan-document       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    495[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      retention rules and applicable state insurance       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    496[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      law                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    497[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Deflection rate vs call-center                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Resolution rate by intent category                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Handoff rate by intent category                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Median time-to-resolution                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Member-satisfaction score by intent                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool-call failure rate per tool                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation-coverage rate (fraction of responses        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    506[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with full citation grounding)                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices (language, channel, plan    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      type, line of business, age, family-relationship,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      representative-completion)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    511[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled review queue]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    512[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of low-           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    513[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      confidence answers, handoff cases, and member-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    514[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      complaint follow-ups                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reviewers tag failure modes (incorrect coverage      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    516[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      answer, incorrect cost estimate, missing             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    517[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      regulatory disclosure, scope violation, citation     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      gap)                                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Compliance-team review for regulatory-disclosure     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      compliance                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: audit trail, telemetry, learning signals]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A few cross-cutting design points specific to the benefits navigator.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Plan-document corpus governance.** The plan documents are versioned governance artifacts. Each plan has a current document set (Summary of Benefits and Coverage, Evidence of Coverage, Schedule of Benefits, formulary, provider directory, member handbook) with effective dates, with re-issuance dates, and with mid-year amendments. The retrieval corpus is rebuilt or incrementally updated when documents change. Each chunk is tagged with plan_id, plan_year, document_type, document_version, section_id, and effective_date. The retrieval query enforces plan-and-year scoping. Stale retrieval (the bot citing the prior plan year's document for a current-year question) is a serious failure mode.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Benefits-data source freshness.** Eligibility, claims, accumulators, prior-auth records, formulary tiers, and provider-network data are pulled from systems-of-record on different cadences. Eligibility refreshes at sub-daily frequency for some payers and at daily frequency for others. Claims data has the date-of-service-to-adjudication lag. Provider-network data updates on at least a monthly cadence with mid-cycle updates as providers join or leave. Formulary updates can happen as often as the PBM publishes them. The bot's tools include the as-of date in every response, and the bot's answers are explicit about freshness ("based on data through April 8, 2026").
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Regulatory-disclosure-phrasings library.** State insurance law, federal law (No Surprises Act, parity, ERISA, ACA, Medicare Advantage rules, Medicaid managed-care rules), and plan-document requirements specify phrasings that must appear in certain communications. The library is owned by the compliance team. The output safety screening verifies that required phrasings are present where the conversation triggers them. State-specific configurations apply where the member's state has additional requirements.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Citation discipline as architectural primitive.** Every coverage assertion, every cost number, every claim-explanation, and every regulatory-rights statement in the bot's response cites the retrieval evidence or the tool output that supports it. The citation is structured (document_version, section_id, retrieval_chunk_id, tool_call_id, as_of_date) and the audit record preserves the citation trail. Members who dispute an answer can be shown the cited evidence; reviewers can verify the answer was grounded.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Cost-estimate-compute as deterministic tool.** The cost-estimate math runs as code over the structured cost-share rules and the member's accumulator state. The tool returns a structured estimate with explicit caveats. The LLM does not compute the math. The audit record stamps the cost-share-rule version, the accumulator-snapshot timestamp, and the negotiated-rate version used.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Member-services routing as a first-class capability.** The bot does not pretend to handle complex appeals, grievances, formal coverage exceptions, or financial-assistance requests. The routing is graceful, with the conversation context attached, and the SLA and escalation procedure to human counselors is explicit. The routing path is exercised in tabletop drills.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    541[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Per-cohort monitoring is non-negotiable.** Resolution rate, handoff rate, citation-coverage rate, member-satisfaction, and intent-classification accuracy vary by language, by channel, by plan type, by line of business, by age cohort, and by representative-vs-direct completion. Per-cohort dashboards are reviewed by the compliance team and the patient-experience team.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **The conversation log is dense PHI plus financial information.** Members ask about medications, diagnoses inferable from procedures, behavioral-health treatments, and bills. The audit, retention, and access-control story matches HIPAA's PHI rules plus any state-specific consumer-financial-information rules.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    546[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Resumability across channels.** A member who starts a conversation in the app, gets pulled away, and comes back through the website should be able to continue. Conversation state is keyed on member_id with channel-specific session metadata, allowing cross-channel continuity for authenticated sessions.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    547[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Disaster-recovery topology.** When the eligibility system, claims system, or formulary system is unreachable, the bot degrades gracefully. The minimum behavior is "I'm having trouble pulling that data right now; would you like me to have someone from member services call you back?" Better: cached recent eligibility responses serve answers with explicit "as-of" disclaimers when the live system is down. Failover behavior is tested quarterly.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ---
