[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1625[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1626[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     Hi, I'm the benefits assistant. I can help
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1627[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          answer questions about your plan, your
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1628[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          claims, your deductible, prior
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1629[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          authorizations, costs, and your medications.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1630[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          I'm a chatbot, not a member services agent,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1631[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          and I can't make formal coverage decisions
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1632[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          or handle appeals on my own. If something
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1633[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          feels like an emergency, please call 911.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1634[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          What can I help you with?
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1635[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1636[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Member:  I got a bill for $1,847 for my wife's knee
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1637[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          MRI, can you explain it?
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1638[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1639[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     Sure, let me take a look. I see Jen had an
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1640[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          MRI on April 8 at Westside Imaging. I'm
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1641[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          pulling the claim now.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1642[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1643[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          Here's what I found. The MRI itself was
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1644[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          processed in-network, and the imaging
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1645[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          center's portion was applied to your
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1646[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          family's deductible. You've used about
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1647[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          $620 of your $3,500 family deductible so
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1648[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          far this year (as of yesterday).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1649[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1650[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          The $1,847 charge you're looking at is from
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1651[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          the radiologist who read the scan,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1652[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          Dr. Lin, who is out-of-network on this
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1653[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          plan even though Westside Imaging is in-
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1654[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          network. This is sometimes called a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1655[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          surprise bill.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1656[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1657[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          Under the federal No Surprises Act, some
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1658[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          out-of-network charges from in-network
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1659[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          facilities are eligible for protection,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1660[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          which generally means you should not owe
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1661[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          more than your in-network cost-share for
