[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1670[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     I'll connect you with our appeals team to
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1671[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          start the process. They'll need a few
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1672[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          details from you. I'm queueing the case
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1673[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          now and someone will reach out to you
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1674[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          within one business day to walk through
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1675[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          the next steps.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1676[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1677[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          Is the phone number ending in 4421 still
